  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Tipston Salvage</strong></u> is a strategic couch co-op logistics game for 1-4 players where you operate a vast number of eclectic junkyards throughout the city of Tipston. Call in new junk, crush and ship metal, and pack the designated storage areas neatly with the correct type of junk. The art of running a junkyard has been lost and it's up to your crew to figure it out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>BUILT FOR TEAMWORK</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every aspect is designed around the concept of working as a team. Communication is key when pulling off a sequence of tasks in sync with your teammates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2afe8c7a9c70508e52f3fe0c3f63d412.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2afe8c7a9c70508e52f3fe0c3f63d412.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2afe8c7a9c70508e52f3fe0c3f63d412.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>IMPROVE YOUR STRATEGY</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each junkyard has its own unique challenges and can take multiple attempts to figure out. Use the Planning Phase at the start of each level to discuss and plan your course of action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/83ee6c42b5dbb90a7e2cf769580f1e27.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/83ee6c42b5dbb90a7e2cf769580f1e27.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/83ee6c42b5dbb90a7e2cf769580f1e27.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DO NOT HANDLE WITH CARE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The junk business is loud and messy. Your truck is fitted with a jet engine that lets you rocket boost into friends and junk alike without the risk of breaking anything. Some recklessness is to be expected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/040b8be629affe6f88b9df2a2997a06d.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/040b8be629affe6f88b9df2a2997a06d.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/040b8be629affe6f88b9df2a2997a06d.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/310acf2186b751760707becc8e87ca88.webp?t=1734617742\" width=612 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>KEY FEATURES:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Designed from the ground up with cooperation in mind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Chaos comes from the players - not from random numbers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Plan your tasks at the start of each level by drawing directly on the screen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Large selection of challenges, ranging from beginner friendly to extreme difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many custom levels made specifically for 2 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Learn to master a uniquely controlled vehicle fitted with a claw and a jet engine</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>AND ALSO:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your truck with paints that can be found hidden or unlocked through challenges </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Optional Leisure Mode that turns off time limits for those who wants to practice or relax </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/310acf2186b751760707becc8e87ca88.webp?t=1734617742\" width=612 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>NOTICE:</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Online Multiplayer is available through Parsec and Steam Remote Play Together    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keyboard controls are supported - Gamepad is recommended </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/310acf2186b751760707becc8e87ca88.webp?t=1734617742\" width=612 height=11 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Tipston Salvage</strong></u> is a strategic couch co-op logistics game for 1-4 players where you operate a vast number of eclectic junkyards throughout the city of Tipston. Call in new junk, crush and ship metal, and pack the designated storage areas neatly with the correct type of junk. The art of running a junkyard has been lost and it's up to your crew to figure it out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/1d1073545a1b20d7fcfb47f0a70353f5.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>BUILT FOR TEAMWORK</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every aspect is designed around the concept of working as a team. Communication is key when pulling off a sequence of tasks in sync with your teammates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2afe8c7a9c70508e52f3fe0c3f63d412.poster.avif?t=1734617742\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2afe8c7a9c70508e52f3fe0c3f63d412.webm?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/2a