steam/apps/1358790/extras/040b8be629affe6f88b9df2a2997a06d.mp4?t=1734617742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/310acf2186b751760707becc8e87ca88.webp?t=1734617742\" width=612 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>KEY FEATURES:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Designed from the ground up with cooperation in mind</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Chaos comes from the players - not from random numbers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Plan your tasks at the start of each level by drawing directly on the screen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Large selection of challenges, ranging from beginner friendly to extreme difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Many custom levels made specifically for 2 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Learn to master a uniquely controlled vehicle fitted with a claw and a jet engine</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>AND ALSO:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your truck with paints that can be found hidden or unlocked through challenges </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Optional Leisure Mode that turns off time limits for those who wants to practice or relax </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358790/extras/310acf2186b751760707becc8e87ca88.webp?t=1734617742\" width=612 height=11 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>NOTICE:</u></